import React, { useEffect } from 'react'; function ImageGallery() { useEffect(() => { const carousel = document.querySelector('.carousel'); const interval = 2000; const advanceCarousel = () => { const carouselItems = carousel.querySelectorAll('.carousel-item'); if (carouselItems.length === 0) return; const currentIndex = Array.from(carouselItems).findIndex(item => item.classList.contains('active')); const nextIndex = currentIndex === -1 ? 0 : (currentIndex === carouselItems.length - 1 ? 0 : currentIndex + 1); carouselItems.forEach(item => item.classList.remove('active')); carouselItems[nextIndex].classList.add('active'); }; const carouselInterval = setInterval(advanceCarousel, interval); return () => clearInterval(carouselInterval); }, []); return ( <>
